{"lastModified":1752593249308,"uri":"c::30234707298::vessel::56a949e0-6449-11ef-ab58-350709999fd5","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Montenegro\n\nStep aboard Catamaran Astrea 42, the latest addition to the Montenegro charter market, offering a luxurious and modern sailing experience. Built in 2024 by the renowned Fountaine Pajot shipyard, this state-of-the-art catamaranis designed for both performance and comfort, making it the perfect choice for those looking to explore the stunning Adriatic coastline.\n\nWith four spacious cabins and four private bathrooms, Astrea 42 is ideal for families, couples, or groups seeking a private catamaran charter in Montenegro. The yacht’s bright and airy interior features a panoramic salon, a fully equipped galley, and large windows that provide stunning sea views. The expansive outdoor areas, including a comfortable cockpit and generous sunbathing spaces, ensure plenty of room for relaxation and socializing while sailing through Montenegro’s breathtaking coastal destinations.\n\nDesigned for smooth and efficient sailing, Catamaran Astrea 42 offers stability, speed, and exceptional handling, making it the perfect vessel for navigating the Bay of Kotor, Budva, and the Luštica Peninsula. Whether you prefer to unwind in a secluded bay, swim in crystal-clear Adriatic waters, or explore Montenegro’s charming seaside towns, this modern catamaran charter in Montenegro provides the ultimate sailing adventure.\n\nNow available for bareboat or skippered charter from Kotor Marina, Astrea 42 is an excellent option for both experienced sailors and those looking for a stress-free voyage with a professional captain. Book your catamaran charter in Montenegro aboard Astrea 42 and enjoy an unforgettable sailing experience along one of Europe’s most scenic coastlines.","blueprint":{"name":"SATELLITE","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::56a949e0-6449-11ef-ab58-350709999fd5::assets::568d78e0-f522-11ef-bf55-61c7a6